心用智慧尋求查究天下所作的一切事，乃知神叫世人所經練的，是極重的勞苦。14. 我見日光之下所作的一切事，都是虛空，都是捕風。<br />\n<br />\n傳道書9:5-6 <br />\n5. 活著的人，知道必死，死了的人，毫無所知，也不再得賞賜，他們的名無人記念。6. 他們的愛，他們的恨，他們的嫉妒，早都消滅了，在日光之下所行的一切事上，他們永不再有分了。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T19:06:04.000Z","msg":"我同意"},{"pid":"a8ed6bb0ede8fab548e8abde41ae1be3d0c519c8","tid":1752983,"uid":322613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T19:17:11.000Z","msg":"最近都思考緊<br />\n<br />\n其實真係冇乜動力再生存<br />\n<br />\n再冇可以令我堅持落去嘅事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d0b833d14f705cc055ced966245c965da6b6e5","tid":1752983,"uid":237186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T19:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94100b0cb0e9b3037b77c2db5c9369e7bdc80d7e","tid":1752983,"uid":325237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T19:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f494bfc7316506a106989137c148f25d0200854","tid":1752983,"uid":3522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da4fcca9c99a9c8872d27d67e3861c1d9250098c","tid":1752983,"uid":11485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e98bef28efe963b1bf765b3e7dc97528d78706f","tid":1752983,"uid":192754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:46:18.000Z","msg":"有咩做完最爽咪做咩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:51:10.000Z","msg":"無"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T19:53:25.000Z","msg":"打飛機呢?"},{"pid":"31c9364032f5d5947c8aa5ebbb04404676930129","tid":1752983,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f494bfc7316506a106989137c148f25d0200854","tid":1752983,"uid":3522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da4fcca9c99a9c8872d27d67e3861c1d9250098c","tid":1752983,"uid":11485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e98bef28efe963b1bf765b3e7dc97528d78706f","tid":1752983,"uid":192754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:46:18.000Z","msg":"有咩做完最爽咪做咩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:51:10.000Z","msg":"無"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T19:53:25.000Z","msg":"打飛機呢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T20:13:24.000Z","msg":"Call g呢？"},{"pid":"4b9c0c4cfe75ee9dc2320e53fb53f79d3b0fb9e6","tid":1752983,"uid":294955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T20:48:22.000Z","msg":"善用自由<br />\n在世make a difference<br />\n祝福別人生命<br />\n即使活得短暫<br />\n也不枉此生"},{"pid":"9c70ddc010338b409bffd1542edf8d11d211aa13","tid":1752983,"uid":313630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T21:38:02.000Z","msg":"好似係永劫輪迴定唔知乜 去對抗呢種虛無<br />\n要去搵一個無論人生會重置幾多次<br />\n都會想遇上 對極都唔厭嘅人<br />\n要去做一件無論人生會重置幾多次<br />\n都仍然會興奮 唔會後悔嘅事<br />\n呢到講緊係重來數億次生命甚至更多<br />\n如果你已經有 咁就係一種意義<br />\n我覺得 意義即係定義你人生嘅必須項<br />\n係永遠永遠不可或缺嘅事物<br />\n<br />\n講開又講 無意義又有咩所謂<br />\n難受咪繼續放空自己 當精神上消失先<br />\n我日日都同自己講可能所謂結束只係重新做人<br />\n咁不如睇下未來會點<br />\n<br />\n利申 一樣覺得人生無意義"},{"pid":"cb9b0a328722d85ca66ae6ed3f40637216a876fd","tid":1752983,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba1862d6a1ebbe061b8bb965a14795d7400945fe","tid":1752983,"uid":11485,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ad0532089da9f931308dfbb97694d626baf0ec9c","tid":1752983,"uid":18265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:28:41.000Z","msg":"人生本身就無意義<br />\n日日忙碌咁生活為咩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:43:00.000Z","msg":"所以我從來唔抗拒自殺呢種行為"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:46:16.000Z","msg":"看來你心中盛載著的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀。人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n<br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，到我們的網站        <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=N9koirI5nbtQ%2BujBUnukpmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=c216a05f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（<a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=N9koirI5nbtQ%2BujBUnukpmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=3fc8e479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。</a> 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"aa0c2bdcd1d6d07e52daef20936562e60cfcd3ce","tid":1752983,"uid":246031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7593423afc0ccca0a4d2f2608beb381ffc9d62bd","tid":1752983,"uid":11485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b43dcedb063ecde1e858573ab225d1ffbe1e2b96","tid":1752983,"uid":246031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:42:46.000Z","msg":"愈嚟愈覺得自己人生冇意義 <br />\n偏偏意義係要自己去尋找&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:21:26.000Z","msg":"大部分人到死一刻都得唔到答案⋯⋯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:39:02.000Z","msg":"有時會諗其實係咪命運嚟 <br />\n可能有啲人天生註定平庸"},{"pid":"b5cbc8b4ef7449d5ff858a8fc27d35af846d31e9","tid":1752983,"uid":55227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa0c2bdcd1d6d07e52daef20936562e60cfcd3ce","tid":1752983,"uid":246031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7593423afc0ccca0a4d2f2608beb381ffc9d62bd","tid":1752983,"uid":11485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b43dcedb063ecde1e858573ab225d1ffbe1e2b96","tid":1752983,"uid":246031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:42:46.000Z","msg":"愈嚟愈覺得自己人生冇意義 <br />\n偏偏意義係要自己去尋找&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:21:26.000Z","msg":"大部分人到死一刻都得唔到答案⋯⋯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:39:02.000Z","msg":"有時會諗其實係咪命運嚟 <br />\n可能有啲人天生註定平庸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T05:09:42.000Z","msg":"根本大部分人都係平庸，<br />\n點樣過好自己平凡ge 一生？"}]}